"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1933446-Lamecha-Girma-injury-Olympics-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Ethiopa's Lamecha Girma needed to be stretchered off track by medics after suffering a horrendous fall in the men's steeplechase final at theParis 2024 Olympicson Wednesday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Girma sprinted into second ahead of his rivals before he appeared to underestimate the jump in front of him.\", \"from\": 177, \"to\": 285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As he leapt over the hurdle, he lost his balance when landing and fell flat onto his front, smashing his head on the ground in a nasty incident.\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 431, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The runner was left laying still on the track while his fellow competitors behind him managed to avoid being collected by the Ethiopian.\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 569, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 559, \"end\": 568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopians\", \"score\": 0.9571059891125926, \"rank\": 0.044795967349470105, \"text\": \"Ethiopian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the track was clear, medical staff quickly rushed to his aid to give him treatment.\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 658, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Girma was later carried off the track with an oxygen mask and a neck brace attached in concerning scenes for spectators, who could only watch on as the 23-year-old long distance runner was taken away for further assessment.\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not yet known what his condition is or the severity of Girma's injury.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 961, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is also no indication as to whether he was conscious following the fall.\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1086, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1151, \"end\": 1156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.99999999936108, \"rank\": 6.389521354166055e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1232, \"end\": 1244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9938633932927828, \"rank\": 0.00617449411426685, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Back in June of 2023, Girma smashed the world record that had stood for 19 years by 1.5 seconds - running the 3,000-metre race in a time of 7:52:11.\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also won the silver medal in the same event at the 2019 World Championships in Doha, the 2022 World Championships in Eugene, and the 2023 World Championships in Budapest.\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1551, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha_Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.6296696724503826, \"rank\": 0.588134292872353, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha_Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha_Diamond_League\"}, {\"begin\": 1633, \"end\": 1641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999734243845335, \"rank\": 2.6576317104421373e-05, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With that pace, he would have been one of the contenders to go for a medal.\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But after his unfortunate trip, the race continued without Girma and was eventually won by Morocco's Soufiane El Bakkali.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1811, \"end\": 1818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\", \"score\": 0.9999569617483185, \"rank\": 4.2996723533236714e-05, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\"}, {\"begin\": 1821, \"end\": 1840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soufiane_El_Bakkali\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Soufiane El Bakkali\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soufiane_El_Bakkali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soufiane_El_Bakkali\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"USA's Kenneth Rooks took silver ahead of Kenya's Abraham Kibiwot, with only a 0.06 second gap to separate the two.\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1959, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1845, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999649895224774, \"rank\": 2.3770947254844084e-05, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1886, \"end\": 1891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999884252462417, \"rank\": 1.1553926737613962e-05, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \